	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" ><img src="images/icons/icon1.gif" border="0" alt=""> <b>Some LOY Charms ...</b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >All <font color="red">Charms</font> so far are <br />
-MAGIC ITEM <br />
-LORE ITEM <br />
-NO DROP<br />
-WT: 0.5 <br />
-Size: TINY<br />
-ALL/ALL<br />
- Stats are given by Lucy or Players and they will vary.<br />
<br />
Sources : The Steel Warrior, EQDruids, Allakhazam, Lucy and random posts <img src="images/smilies/wink.gif" border="0" alt=""> <br />
<br />
(Feel free to post info, corrections or new <font color="red">charms</font> if you get some)<br />
