166 Agi & Dex = AC +1 MR +2 DR +2 PR +2<br />
305 Agi & Dex = AC +3 MR +13 DR +13 PR +13<br />
- Grants a bonus as you gain agility and dexterity <br />
* Galikor Sevalin (can spawn on any high seas assassin spot or at the tavern (not the one with the troubadour)<br />
# Dulak Harbor<br />
<br />
