305 Dex & 355 Int = STA +11 CHA +11 Mana +27 FR +7<br />
- High Int Dex<br />
* Emissary of Hate<br />
# Dulak's Harbor, in the last room with the Crypt in the middle of the Hate Tunnel<br />
