<br />
<b> Charm of the Brotherhood</b> <br />
AC +1 HP +5 Mana +5 MR +2 (PER SAME CLASS IN GROUP)<br />
-Improves when you are grouped with others of the same class. <br />
* Talk to Firon Dernkal in Neriak and collect for him all four copper, silver, gold, and platinum "Medallion of Service"'s dropping in Dulak<br />
<br />
<br />
<b> Insignia of the Emerald Warrior</b> <br />
Warmly faction = AC +1 DEX +5 HP +9 DR +9<br />
Ally faction = AC +2 DEX +5 HP +10 DR +10<br />
- Improves as your faction with the Emerald Warriors increases<br />
* Talk to Faerik Windrunner in Kelethin and collect things<br />
Link : <a href="Http://forums.interealms.com/ranger/showthread.php?threadid=19320" target="_blank">Http://forums.interealms.com/ranger...?threadid=19320</a><br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
<b> Xoomix's Mystical Charm </b> <br />
Str +8 Mana +25 <br />
Effect: Extended Range II<br />
- Grants a bonus as you gain dexterity<br />
