	<td bgcolor="#404070" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" ><img src="images/icons/icon1.gif" border="0" alt=""> <b></b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >Platinum Disc goes in the charm slot.  I recently obtained one and tested it by moving platinum between my account and my wife's account.  Here's what I found.<br />
<br />
With this amount (in thousands of platinum pieces) in bank, it had these stats:<br />
<br />
0k no stats<br />
5k +1 hp +1 mana<br />
10k +3 hp +3 mana +1 fr +1 cr<br />
15k +1 dex +4 hp +4 mana +1 fr +1 cr<br />
20k +1 dex +6 hp +6 mana +2 fr +2 cr<br />
25k +1 dex +5 hp +5 mana +1 fr +1 cr<br />
30k +3 hp +3 mana +1 fr +1 cr                                              <br />
40k no stats<br />
60k +1 dex +5 hp +5 mana +1 fr +1 cr<br />
80k +1 hp +1 mana<br />
416k +1 dex +3 hp +3 mana +1 fr +1 cr<br />
<br />
<br />
-Bolas</font></p>
	
	<p><p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >__________________<br>
