	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" ><img src="images/icons/icon1.gif" border="0" alt=""> <b>Gold Pin</b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >Siilvir,<br />
<br />
Well, I used to carry around the 5360pp, but it just got to be a hassle that I can't loot all to much, so I dropped it down to 4000pp now.   There's a number slightly over 4k (around 4300 or so) that gives AC 3 STA +7 MANA +21? MR +4, but by carrying 4k around, I get a slightly lowered # (sta 6, etc) and I still have the freedom to loot whatever I have.  As for weight probs, I have Bobbing Corpse (Bauble clicky) most of the time so I don't take falling damage.  w/o plat my normal weight is around 97/220ish, so carrying the money's not a prob with all the WR bags I have.  And worst comes to worst, I can summon up my GM Smithy Bags (10 slot, Giant, 100% WR) and stuff junk in there.  I haven't really experimented too much w/ the lower amounts, but I do know that @ 500pp on you, you get a whopping 1hp.  lol.  and it tiers up from there.<br />
<br />
As for the mask that I'm wearing, honestly, I bought it in the bazaar so I'm not quite sure where it drops.  Traded my "extra" CoCW for it - dunno if that was a good deal or not.  Anyhow, I just checked Alla & it doesn't have any drop info on it.<br />
<br />
hope this helps a bit.</font></p>
	
